code: @Override public boolean wasDiscoveredBy(Class<? extends EndpointDiscoverer<?, ?>> discoverer) {     return discoverer.isInstance(this.discoverer). }

@Override public String toString() {     ToStringCreator creator = new ToStringCreator(this).append("discoverer", this.discoverer.getClass().getName()).append("endpointBean", this.endpointBean.getClass().getName()).     appendFields(creator).     return creator.toString(). }
